{"word":"G4112 - πλαστός - plastós - plas-tos' - Feigned","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πλαστός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">plastós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">plas-tos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Feigned</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தந்திரமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. moulded, formed"},{"paragraph":"2. feigned"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4111 - πλάσσω - plássō - plas'-so/4111\">G4111</a>; <i>moulded</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>artificial</i> or (figuratively) <i>fictitious</i> (<i>false</i>): - feigned.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4110/4110\">G4110</a>, <a href=\"#/G4111/4111\">G4111</a>, <a href=\"#/G4112/4112\">G4112</a>"}]}